item.title: Kevin Bonds
item.description: Strong analytics generalist with depth in many technical areas. Experience applying industry best tech (SQL, Teradata, R, Python, Git, Shiny, Hadoop, Zeppelin, GCP, ODBC, JDBC, JWT, Outh2.0) to data analysis, data engineering validation, and data product design. Influencer for collaborative work flows and analytics best practices. Always curious and flexible with methods, tools, and techniques to add business value at minimal expense.
